Yeah, I can't see why not.

00:19:45.400 --> 00:19:51.719
I personally am not super familiar with, I don't know, I'm assuming things like Azure.

00:19:52.000 --> 00:19:58.280
I'm not really familiar with that, but I see no reason why these couldn't be generalized

00:19:58.280 --> 00:20:00.280
for other cloud providers, definitely.

